          <h3> Research interests</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><b>Main areas of research :</b> Low dimensional topology, Combinatorics, Geometric group theory, Representation theory, Number Theory, Arithmetic Dynamics.<br> 
			</li>
			<li><b>Other areas of interests :</b> all the rest, but especially Dynamics, Game theory, and Physics.<br> 
			</li>
			<li><b>Research statements and projects :</b> 
